<div class="container">
    <h1>Animatsiyalar bo'limiga xush kelibsiz.</h1>
    <p>Bu yerda fizika fanini zamonaviy axborot texnologiyalari orqali media ko'rinishda turli xil animatsiya hamda virtual labaratoriyalar orqali o'rganishingiz mumkin!
    </p>
    <p>Animatsiyalar va virtual labaratoriyalar asosan TATU universiteti virtual hamda <a href="">phet</a> online platformasi orqali olingan
    </p>
    <div class="cards container row ">
        {{#each animations}}
            <div class="card col-xl-3 col-md-6 mx-1 mt-1 p-0">
                <img class="card-img-top" style="object-fit: cover; width: 100%; min-height: 200px"
                    src="{{previewPicture}}"
                    alt="Card image cap">
                <div class="card-body d-flex justify-content-between flex-column">
                    <h5 class="card-title">{{title}}</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">{{preview}}</p>
                    <a href="/animations/{{_id}}" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Olg'a</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>